description: Take list of cubes, move left digit of each term to end of previous term.
links: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
prog: (Haskell)a032761 n = a032761_list !! na032761_list = 0 : map read (zipWith (++) vs (tail us)) :: [Integer]   where (us,vs) = unzip $ map ((splitAt 1) . show) a000578_list-- _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Oct 10 2013
